    "What language is the data that the model is trained on?",
    "LLMs are trained on very large amounts of text data.",
    "It is important to know what text it is trained on to be aware of the biases inherent in the model and how to adjust accordingly.",
    "LLMs are biased because of the biased choice of texts that are used to train the model (Navigli et al 2023).",
    "In other words, the texts themselves are not representative."
